Super Bowl 2023 is finally upon us. The Kansas City Chiefs and Philadelphia Eagles will finally take the field in Glendale, Ariz. after two weeks of drama and prognostication. Patrick Mahomes is looking for his second Super Bowl title in four years, while the Eagles are looking to win for the second time in six years, this time with a new quarterback in Jalen Hurts and new head coach in Nick Sirianni. Rihanna will perform during the Super Bowl halftime show and Chris Stapleton will sing the national anthem, with all the typical pageantry surrounding the most-watched event in the country every year. Follow along for live updates throughout Super Bowl 2023.